   value=""/><BODY><TEXT>&lt;p&gt;The&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Learning and Assessment Plan (LAP)&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;document attached is your key to knowing what is being taught and when.&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;It outlines the resources you need for the course, how you will be assessed and when those assessments are due.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;If your Learning and Assessment Plan is not here,&amp;nbsp;please contact your lecturer.&lt;/p&gt;</TEXT><TYPE
